title: OnePlus 10 Pro arrives in North America, other markets by ‘the end of March’
content:
After launching exclusively in China earlier this year, OnePlus has finally confirmed a launch date for the OnePlus 10 Pro in North America. The phone is apparently set to arrive within the next month.

more…

The post OnePlus 10 Pro arrives in North America, other markets by ‘the end of March’ appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: Straight from the source, the OnePlus 10 Pro's launch date has been confirmed as sometime in March 2022 for North America, Europe, and India.
